{"tid":1112062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港TB嘅明天]達拉斯跨性別女撞車欲逃走 遭圍觀者暴打","createTime":"2019-04-17T08:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T13:12:29.000Z","uid":65346,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aedc224b93c5a6d0a05c16ac7980088a2982c6d7","tid":1112062,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190417/59497779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F59497779&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=f38dc3cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190417%2F59497779&h=53f79eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190417/59497779</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國達拉斯（Dallas）日前發生暴力事件，一名非裔跨性別女子觸發交通意外後想逃走，有人付錢指使一名圍觀者毆打她，其他圍觀市民不但未勸阻，甚至有人趁亂狠踢已倒地的受害者，最後數名女性挺身阻止，受害者才脫身。警方目前已逮捕一名疑犯，動機不排除是仇恨犯罪。<br />\n <br />\n記者：林宜萱<br />\n<br />\n《Buzzfeed新聞網》報道，跨性人士布克（Muhlaysia Booker）上周五與人發生輕微交通事故，其後有人付200美元給圍觀者湯馬斯（Edward Thomas），要他出手毆打布克。湯馬斯上前將布克推倒在地上、連環揮拳毆打，並以性別歧視的粗口辱罵她。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，布克肇事後想要逃走，現場至少兩名男子趁機猛踩布克的頭部。布克護住頭部、起身想逃走時，湯馬斯仍繼續追打。數名女性擋到兩人中間後，湯馬斯才停手。<br />\n<br />\n警方周日逮捕湯馬斯，仍在追查是誰付錢給他。湯馬斯保釋金高達7.5萬美元，目前還押。"},{"pid":"8cfab5bf8e2cb187f0d8c4bdfa18e7f111aadf23","tid":1112062,"uid":17103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"關 TB 咩事 .. 佢係男變女 ..."},{"pid":"6d8474dac29ab51ac6c3a043ecca9761c16b56ff","tid":1112062,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"其後有人付200美元給圍觀者湯馬斯（Edward Thomas）<br />\n要他出手毆打布克<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔睇內容以為因為見係基佬所以打穫佢"},{"pid":"be11cd848bd7fa8454d2477b408209363620cebd","tid":1112062,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"不排除是仇恨犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚野仇恨犯罪 又嚟思想警察"},{"pid":"1231fdac20a5beaa0f731ab0f760c10ef264bba6","tid":1112062,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"btw Buzzfeed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}